  "texts": [
    "The results are presented in Fig. 5b, c, from which several conclusions can be drawn.",
    "First, DH-LIF neurons improve the capability of handling temporal heterogeneity with higher accuracy.",
    "Second, compared to one-layer SFNNs, two-layer SFNNs and onelayer SRNNs demonstrate much better performance owing to the interneuron integration of temporal features.",
    "Third, DH-SFNNs and DH-SRNNs gradually produce higher accuracy as the number of dendritic branches grows.",
    "In short, these results evidence the improved capability of performing multi-timescale temporal computing tasks benefited from the temporal dendritic heterogeneity, and further reveal the synergistic working mechanism of the neuron-level and network-level feature integration."
  ],
